videos.headline: Illinois connects on the deep ball for the TD
videos.description: Illinois quarterback Wes Lunt has all sorts of time and takes advantage of it hitting Malik Turner for a 68-yard touchdown, and Turner's second of the game to increase the Illini's lead to 14-0 over Murray State.
